Question number2 : EM Algorithm

1. Use the below command to run the program

	python q2.py --! #randomrestartcount --i #iterations -HJ TRAIN

	or

	python q2.py

	This will set the default values to all the above arguments
	#random restarts = 30
	#iterationcount = 40
	filename = 'TRAIN'

Question number3 : Processing COPIALE corpus using EM Algorithm

2. Use the below command to run the program

	python q2.py --! #randomrestartcount --i #iterations -HJ COPIALE.txt

	or

	python q2.py

	This will set the default values to all the above arguments
	#random restarts = 30
	#iterationcount = 40
	filename = 'COPIALE.txt'
